            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> baioli <lb n="2"/>et <expan><abbr>vexillari</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> col<lb break="no" n="3"/>legio Victorien<lb break="no" n="4"/>sium signifer<lb break="no" n="5"/>orum Genium d<lb break="no" n="6"/>e suo fecerunt <lb n="7"/>VIIII <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Octobr</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Pr<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>esente</abbr></expan> et Albino <lb n="9"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>estituerunt</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Paternus <lb n="2"/>Prudens <lb n="3"/>Marianus <lb n="4"/>Dagovassus <lb n="5"/>Cerialis <lb n="6"/>Aturo <lb n="7"/>Victor </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Satullus <lb n="2"/>Sattara <lb n="3"/>Macrinus <lb n="4"/>Laetus <lb n="5"/>Apollinaris <lb n="6"/>Secundanus <lb n="7"/>Ursus
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Basis die Statuette eines Genius mit Mauerkrone; die Inschriften verteilen sich auf die Vorderseite, die linke und die rechte Nebenseite der Basis. Höhe der Basis mit Statuette: 50,5 cm. Schreibtechnik: eingraviert.</p>
            </div>
